{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Legally require lingerie-specific fitting rooms to be women-only",
        "additional_details": "To ensure the safeguarding of young girls and women in lingerie-specific fitting rooms. Lingerie bra fittings are intimate and personal and leave the women and young girls in a vulnerable position. Whether it be their first fitting or they have undergone a mastectomy and they now need a post-surgical fitting. All women deserve the privacy and respect that is owed to them during these fittings. Allowing men into these specific fitting rooms undermines all safeguarding and increases risk of safety.",
        "background": "Legally require that lingerie-specific fitting rooms are reserved exclusively for women.",
